A '''J9 worker drone'''<ref name="By the numbers">{{SWKidsYouTube|series=Star Wars By the Numbers|text=Every Droid in Star Wars|video=UQg6aX7lqTA|nolive=1}}</ref> was a type of [[droid]] with a pointed face and large [[insect]]-like [[eye]]s<ref name="Join the Resistance" /> resembling those of the [[Verpine]] [[species]].<ref name="Always Bet on Chop">{{RebelsMagCite|23|Always Bet on Chop}}</ref> The "[[monster droid]]" [[AG-90]] had the head of a J9.<ref name="Join the Resistance" /> [[BG-J38]] was another J9 worker drone affiliated with [[Jabba's criminal empire|Jabba Desilijic Tiure's criminal empire]].<ref name="SWCT ROTJ">{{Topps|set=2020 Topps Star Wars Black & White: Return of the Jedi|subset=Behind the Scenes|cardname=BG-J38}}</ref>

